{
  "stem": "10478.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that way she started to write my book.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Janet Keith.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Janet Keith, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I visited her once or twice a week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't know the computer word processor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did it on an old IBM.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she just typed the whole story, what I told her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, a week later, she wrote it down a week later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We re-read it, and we corrected it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so-- And what she did, of course, I give-- I supplied her with all the addresses for the Jewish people in Maastricht and also in Israel, and in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she wrote them letters asking for their report.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that, she make, combined into one book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a couple of years, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A couple of years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is the title of the book?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was my story, yes, and the story of the people I helped, also, yeah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't think that it-- I think they sold out now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it is in the libraries, here, and also in the Jewish library in-- in community halls around here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when was it published?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1992, I believe, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1992.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you know what happened to the Jews that you sheltered?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened to them later on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you  know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I keep in contact with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And usually with the Jewish new year, I send them a card or  a letter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I get, with our Christmas, a letter back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- and then we've gone three times I went to Israel for a visit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The first time, I went with a tourist group and let them know that I was coming to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had a reunion in the Hilton Hotel in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
